    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/889acbb914f6dab135b40158fbfd9a6c.avif?t=1771347450\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/becc2afc6a944d4c22e6c830d3401573.poster.avif?t=1771347450\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/becc2afc6a944d4c22e6c830d3401573.webm?t=1771347450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/becc2afc6a944d4c22e6c830d3401573.mp4?t=1771347450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Crypt Custodian》是一款以净化冥界为背景、引人入胜的类银河恶魔城/塞尔达传说游戏。<br><br>你将扮演布鲁托——这只淘气的猫咪刚刚死去，来到了冥界的王宫。在与冥界守护者肯德拉进行简短且灾难性的会面后，你被赶出了王宫，还被判处承担净化任务...永远如此！<br><br>探索王宫周边的广阔区域，凭借你信赖的扫帚与猛兽战斗，并掌握新技能，拓展你所处的世界。破解谜题，探索秘密，还有...策划一场伏击，打回王宫去！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/6ee267a202f36fef9745c66d4d2d4e02.poster.avif?t=1771347450\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/6ee267a202f36fef9745c66d4d2d4e02.webm?t=1771347450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/6ee267a202f36fef9745c66d4d2d4e02.mp4?t=1771347450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394650/extras/326a49863f89f64f4b7959642f69b4d1.avif?t=1771347450\" width=600 height=102 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >众多富有魅力的角色</h2>结识徘徊在王宫外的其他各种邪恶幽灵。了解他们如何丧生，以及为何面临永恒的惩罚！还可前往当地幽魂出没之所——罪人酒馆，与你遇到的幽灵交谈，并升级你的装备。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >数不胜数的升级</h2>破解谜题，击败史诗头目并坚持不懈地清理破败的地下城，以收集全新的升级和技能。通过混搭升级来定制你的游戏风格，并利用收集到的技能拓展你所在的世界。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >热热闹闹的互联世界</h2>在所到之处都藏有秘密的广袤世界里游荡。构建你自己的路线，按照自己的节奏探索冥界的无数秘密。",
